purpose: To offer an interactive user interface that visualizes and enhances the functionality of the CrewAI package.
principle: Built using modern web technologies to create a dynamic and interactive UI for visualizing AI model outputs and configurations.
reusability: Designed as a standalone interface that can be integrated with the CrewAI package, offering extensibility through modular components and API endpoints.
limitations: Primarily dependent on the CrewAI package for core functionalities, limited to the features supported by CrewAI.
name: CrewAI-Visualizer
description: Interactive user interface for CrewAI package.
highlight: Provides an interactive visualization interface specifically designed for the CrewAI package, enhancing user interaction with AI models.
